  "prompt": "What is the definition of dude?",
  "response": "The term \"dude\" is an informal slang word that is commonly used to refer to a person, typically a male, but it can also be used in a gender-neutral manner. Its origins date back to the late 19th century, where it initially referred to a man who was overly concerned with his dress and appearance. Over time, \"dude\" evolved into a more general term of address or reference for a person, often conveying a sense of coolness or camaraderie. It can also be used as a term of affection among friends. In modern usage, \"dude\" is often associated with a laid-back, casual style of communication.",
